// 인체 이미지용 기본 SVG 이미지 데이터
export const bodyImageSvgs = {
  front: `data:image/svg+xml;base64,${btoa(`
    <svg width="200" height="400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <style>
        .body-outline { fill: none; stroke: #333; stroke-width: 2; }
        .body-fill { fill: #f0f0f0; stroke: #333; stroke-width: 1; }
      </style>
      
      <!-- 머리 -->
      <circle cx="100" cy="40" r="25" class="body-fill"/>
      
      <!-- 목 -->
      <rect x="90" y="60" width="20" height="20" class="body-fill"/>
      
      <!-- 몸통 -->
      <ellipse cx="100" cy="140" rx="45" ry="60" class="body-fill"/>
      
      <!-- 팔 -->
      <ellipse cx="60" cy="110" rx="12" ry="40" class="body-fill"/>
      <ellipse cx="140" cy="110" rx="12" ry="40" class="body-fill"/>
      <ellipse cx="45" cy="170" rx="10" ry="35" class="body-fill"/>
      <ellipse cx="155" cy="170" rx="10" ry="35" class="body-fill"/>
      
      <!-- 다리 -->
      <ellipse cx="80" cy="240" rx="15" ry="45" class="body-fill"/>
      <ellipse cx="120" cy="240" rx="15" ry="45" class="body-fill"/>
      <ellipse cx="80" cy="320" rx="12" ry="45" class="body-fill"/>
      <ellipse cx="120" cy="320" rx="12" ry="45" class="body-fill"/>
      
      <!-- 발 -->
      <ellipse cx="75" cy="375" rx="15" ry="8" class="body-fill"/>
      <ellipse cx="125" cy="375" rx="15" ry="8" class="body-fill"/>
      
      <!-- 관절점 표시 -->
      <circle cx="100" cy="65" r="3" fill="#666"/>  <!-- 목 -->
      <circle cx="100" cy="80" r="3" fill="#666"/>  <!-- 어깨 중심 -->
      <circle cx="75" cy="85" r="3" fill="#666"/>   <!-- 왼쪽 어깨 -->
      <circle cx="125" cy="85" r="3" fill="#666"/>  <!-- 오른쪽 어깨 -->
      <circle cx="60" cy="130" r="3" fill="#666"/>  <!-- 왼쪽 팔꿈치 -->
      <circle cx="140" cy="130" r="3" fill="#666"/> <!-- 오른쪽 팔꿈치 -->
      <circle cx="45" cy="200" r="3" fill="#666"/>  <!-- 왼쪽 손목 -->
      <circle cx="155" cy="200" r="3" fill="#666"/> <!-- 오른쪽 손목 -->
      <circle cx="85" cy="200" r="3" fill="#666"/>  <!-- 왼쪽 골반 -->
      <circle cx="115" cy="200" r="3" fill="#666"/> <!-- 오른쪽 골반 -->
      <circle cx="80" cy="280" r="3" fill="#666"/>  <!-- 왼쪽 무릎 -->
      <circle cx="120" cy="280" r="3" fill="#666"/> <!-- 오른쪽 무릎 -->
      <circle cx="80" cy="360" r="3" fill="#666"/>  <!-- 왼쪽 발목 -->
      <circle cx="120" cy="360" r="3" fill="#666"/> <!-- 오른쪽 발목 -->
      
      <text x="100" y="390" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" fill="#666">정면</text>
    </svg>
  `)}`,
  
  spine: `data:image/svg+xml;base64,${btoa(`
    <svg width="200" height="400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <style>
        .spine-line { fill: none; stroke: #333; stroke-width: 3; }
        .vertebra { fill: #666; stroke: #333; stroke-width: 1; }
        .body-outline { fill: #f0f0f0; stroke: #333; stroke-width: 1; opacity: 0.3; }
      </style>
      
      <!-- 몸통 실루엣 -->
      <ellipse cx="100" cy="140" rx="40" ry="60" class="body-outline"/>
      
      <!-- 척추선 -->
      <line x1="100" y1="65" x2="100" y2="200" class="spine-line"/>
      
      <!-- 경추 (C1-C7) -->
      <circle cx="100" cy="70" r="4" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="80" r="4" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="90" r="4" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="4" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="110" r="4" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="120" r="4" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="130" r="4" class="vertebra"/>
      
      <!-- 흉추 (T1-T12) -->
      <circle cx="100" cy="140" r="5" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="150" r="5" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="160" r="5" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="170" r="5" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="180" r="5" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="190" r="5" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="200" r="5" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="210" r="5" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="220" r="5" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="230" r="5" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="240" r="5" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="250" r="5" class="vertebra"/>
      
      <!-- 요추 (L1-L5) -->
      <circle cx="100" cy="260" r="6" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="270" r="6" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="280" r="6" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="290" r="6" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="300" r="6" class="vertebra"/>
      
      <!-- 천추/미추 -->
      <circle cx="100" cy="310" r="5" class="vertebra"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="320" r="4" class="vertebra"/>
      
      <!-- 라벨 -->
      <text x="120" y="75" font-size="10" fill="#666">C1-C7</text>
      <text x="120" y="195" font-size="10" fill="#666">T1-T12</text>
      <text x="120" y="275" font-size="10" fill="#666">L1-L5</text>
      <text x="120" y="315" font-size="10" fill="#666">천추</text>
      
      <text x="100" y="390" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" fill="#666">척추 측면</text>
    </svg>
  `)}`,
  
  back: `data:image/svg+xml;base64,${btoa(`
    <svg width="200" height="400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <style>
        .body-outline { fill: none; stroke: #333; stroke-width: 2; }
        .body-fill { fill: #f0f0f0; stroke: #333; stroke-width: 1; }
      </style>
      
      <!-- 머리 -->
      <circle cx="100" cy="40" r="25" class="body-fill"/>
      
      <!-- 목 -->
      <rect x="90" y="60" width="20" height="20" class="body-fill"/>
      
      <!-- 몸통 -->
      <ellipse cx="100" cy="140" rx="45" ry="60" class="body-fill"/>
      
      <!-- 팔 -->
      <ellipse cx="60" cy="110" rx="12" ry="40" class="body-fill"/>
      <ellipse cx="140" cy="110" rx="12" ry="40" class="body-fill"/>
      <ellipse cx="45" cy="170" rx="10" ry="35" class="body-fill"/>
      <ellipse cx="155" cy="170" rx="10" ry="35" class="body-fill"/>
      
      <!-- 다리 -->
      <ellipse cx="80" cy="240" rx="15" ry="45" class="body-fill"/>
      <ellipse cx="120" cy="240" rx="15" ry="45" class="body-fill"/>
      <ellipse cx="80" cy="320" rx="12" ry="45" class="body-fill"/>
      <ellipse cx="120" cy="320" rx="12" ry="45" class="body-fill"/>
      
      <!-- 발 -->
      <ellipse cx="75" cy="375" rx="15" ry="8" class="body-fill"/>
      <ellipse cx="125" cy="375" rx="15" ry="8" class="body-fill"/>
      
      <!-- 등 근육 라인 -->
      <line x1="85" y1="90" x2="85" y2="180" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/>
      <line x1="115" y1="90" x2="115" y2="180" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/>
      <line x1="100" y1="85" x2="100" y2="190" stroke="#666" stroke-width="2"/>
      
      <!-- 견갑골 -->
      <ellipse cx="80" cy="110" rx="15" ry="25" fill="none" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/>
      <ellipse cx="120" cy="110" rx="15" ry="25" fill="none" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/>
      
      <!-- 관절점 표시 -->
      <circle cx="100" cy="65" r="3" fill="#666"/>  <!-- 목 -->
      <circle cx="75" cy="85" r="3" fill="#666"/>   <!-- 왼쪽 어깨 -->
      <circle cx="125" cy="85" r="3" fill="#666"/>  <!-- 오른쪽 어깨 -->
      <circle cx="60" cy="130" r="3" fill="#666"/>  <!-- 왼쪽 팔꿈치 -->
      <circle cx="140" cy="130" r="3" fill="#666"/> <!-- 오른쪽 팔꿈치 -->
      <circle cx="45" cy="200" r="3" fill="#666"/>  <!-- 왼쪽 손목 -->
      <circle cx="155" cy="200" r="3" fill="#666"/> <!-- 오른쪽 손목 -->
      <circle cx="85" cy="200" r="3" fill="#666"/>  <!-- 왼쪽 골반 -->
      <circle cx="115" cy="200" r="3" fill="#666"/> <!-- 오른쪽 골반 -->
      <circle cx="80" cy="280" r="3" fill="#666"/>  <!-- 왼쪽 무릎 -->
      <circle cx="120" cy="280" r="3" fill="#666"/> <!-- 오른쪽 무릎 -->
      <circle cx="80" cy="360" r="3" fill="#666"/>  <!-- 왼쪽 발목 -->
      <circle cx="120" cy="360" r="3" fill="#666"/> <!-- 오른쪽 발목 -->
      
      <text x="100" y="390" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" fill="#666">후면</text>
    </svg>
  `)}`,
};

export default bodyImageSvgs;
